root: ^Hi!What a great day! Is everything going well?
^Are you okay? I'ts okay if you're tired, you can be honest with me.
^That last few days have been so hard, you know. I barely feel like I know what I'm doing sometimes.
^I get that. Do you think you need a break?
^No. I just need to work harder.
^That isn't always the answer, you know. You can't just distract your stress with work. That just creates more stress.
^But I've been doing this job for so long, the fact that I'm feeling stressed now just means that I'm not good enough.
^That's not what that means. It's not healthy-
^But stress makes a lot of things make sense. I can't even remember how long I've been working here because of how stressed I am.
^You're putting too much on yourself. you should take a break.
